body.paragraph:
‘‘Evaṃ vutte, kevaṭṭa, cātumahārājikā devā taṃ bhikkhuṃ  etadavocuṃ – ‘mayampi kho, bhikkhu, na jānāma, yatthime cattāro mahābhūtā aparisesā nirujjhanti, seyyathidaṃ – pathavīdhātu āpodhātu tejodhātu vāyodhātūtivāyodhātu. atthi kho 
Note { id=0, line='3', referenceLine='25', original='vāyodhātu. atthi kho (pī. evamuparipi)', type='auto', previous=' etadavocuṃ – ‘mayampi kho, bhikkhu, na jānāma, yatthime cattāro mahābhūtā aparisesā nirujjhanti, seyyathidaṃ – pathavīdhātu āpodhātu tejodhātu vāyodhātūti '
	Alternative{lang='vri', text='vāyodhātūti'}
	Alternative{lang='pī. evamuparipi', text='vāyodhātu. atthi kho'}}
. Atthi kho 
Note { id=1, line='12', referenceLine='25', original='vāyodhātu. atthi kho (pī. evamuparipi)', type='auto', previous='. Atthi kho '
	Alternative{lang='vri', text='Atthi kho'}
	Alternative{lang='pī. evamuparipi', text='vāyodhātu. atthi kho'}}
, bhikkhu, cattāro mahārājāno amhehi abhikkantatarā ca paṇītatarā ca. Te kho etaṃ jāneyyuṃ, yatthime cattāro mahābhūtā aparisesā nirujjhanti, seyyathidaṃ – pathavīdhātu āpodhātu tejodhātu vāyodhātū’ti.

‘‘Evaṃ vutte, ahaṃ, kevaṭṭa, taṃ bhikkhuṃ etadavocaṃ – ‘bhūtapubbaṃ, bhikkhu, sāmuddikā vāṇijā tīradassiṃ sakuṇaṃ gahetvā nāvāya samuddaṃ ajjhogāhanti. Te atīradakkhiniyā nāvāya tīradassiṃ sakuṇaṃ muñcanti. So gacchateva puratthimaṃ disaṃ, gacchati dakkhiṇaṃ disaṃ, gacchati pacchimaṃ disaṃ, gacchati uttaraṃ disaṃ, gacchati uddhaṃ disaṃ, gacchati anudisaṃ. Sace so samantā tīraṃ  passati, tathāgatakovatathāpakkantova 
Note { id=2, line='21', referenceLine='38', original='tathāpakkantova (syā.)', type='auto', previous=' passati, tathāgatakova '
	Alternative{lang='vri', text='tathāgatakova'}
	Alternative{lang='syā.', text='tathāpakkantova'}}
hoti. Sace pana so samantā tīraṃ na passati, tameva nāvaṃ paccāgacchati. Evameva kho tvaṃ, bhikkhu, yato yāva brahmalokā pariyesamāno imassa pañhassa veyyākaraṇaṃ nājjhagā, atha mamaññeva santike paccāgato. Na kho eso, bhikkhu, pañho evaṃ pucchitabbo – ‘kattha nu kho, bhante, ime cattāro mahābhūtā aparisesā nirujjhanti, seyyathidaṃ – pathavīdhātu āpodhātu tejodhātu vāyodhātū’ti?
